  "detailed_description": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817200/extras/cc8d85a66cc0553bd97864c04bc3750b.webp?t=1656620686\" width=282 height=43 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817200/extras/3dc0844cb6c6ad7639c3123b12f855eb.avif?t=1656620686\" width=287 height=66 /></span><br><br><strong>this House</strong> uniquely blends single player RPG exploration, hand-drawn art, puzzle solving, surreal humour and a creepy atmosphere.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817200/extras/615d5e1cf81251807b1e10a3470e8ebc.poster.avif?t=1656620686\" width=680 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817200/extras/615d5e1cf81251807b1e10a3470e8ebc.webm?t=1656620686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817200/extras/615d5e1cf81251807b1e10a3470e8ebc.mp4?t=1656620686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817200/extras/3d2b5e51de6302b4a6599703c30a3903.webp?t=1656620686\" width=282 height=43 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Discover the mysteries and secrets of this House through exploration and puzzle solving<br></li><li> Logical and lateral thinking is required to solve the many <strong>devious puzzles</strong> <br></li><li> A unique <strong>hand drawn</strong> art style<br></li><li> An unusual take on <strong>crafting </strong>where multiple items can be combined</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817200/extras/0e03abd1a2da517cf8d7281409ceb399.webp?t=1656620686\" width=282 height=43 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817200/extras/bdcb8a6895ba6a4b18c52c36b15aaa1d.avif?t=1656620686\" width=641 height=98 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A choice of characters to choose from at the start with more to unlock</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817200/extras/099adc3b63ad0b5914f4cda40cdc7eb1.webp?t=1656620686\" width=282 height=43 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> An original <strong>atmospheric soundtrack</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817200/extras/d10002183c99adb5b02976f5875a7f74.webp?t=1656620686\" width=282 height=43 /></span><br>A variety of unique <strong>arcade style minigames</strong> based on the main story. These feature:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Shoot the Skulls:</strong> Use a plant pot to fire a tennis ball at skulls <br><i>(Just a normal day at the office)</i><br></li><li> <strong>Skull Sweeper </strong>: Use your brain to move the skulls to the correct colours</li></ul>",
